  "category": "infrastructure",
  "description": "Add a `.coderabbit.yaml` configuration file to enable automated code review on all PRs.\n\n## What to do\n\nCreate `.coderabbit.yaml` at the repository root with:\n- Language: TypeScript (Lit web components focus)\n- Path instructions for `packages/hx-library/` — enforce no hardcoded values, require a11y tests, require CEM updates\n- Path instructions for `apps/admin/` — React + Next.js + Tailwind conventions\n- Path instructions for `apps/docs/` — Astro/Starlight documentation completeness\n- Auto-review settings: summarize changes, suggest test additions for untested code\n- Tone: professional, focus on enterprise healthcare quality bar\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n- `.coderabbit.yaml` exists at repo root\n- Configuration targets Lit WC library conventions\n- Path-specific rules cover all major workspaces\n- File is committed and reviewable",
